Name: Handshakes
About the game: Handshakes is a short and sweet puzzler where you must guide two hands towards their goal of a warm, firm handshake. Play by yourself, or share your keyboard/controller with a friend and play through 30 puzzles that are designed to stretch your brain, not strain it.
